Maintainer: Thais Vasconcelos <tvasc@umich.edu>
Imports: magick, rgbif, sf
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
Description: This package provides tools designed to search and download metadata and openly available images associated with herbarium specimens based on taxon or geographical area. Tools included in the package are described in more detail in Vasconcelos and Boyko (2024; doi:10.1101/2024.08.25.609600).
